Package PayrollProcessing

Class Management

  • java.lang.Object
    • PayrollProcessing.Employee
      • PayrollProcessing.Fulltime
        • PayrollProcessing.Management
  • public class Management
extends Fulltime
    The Management class extends the Fulltime class, holding the salary values through the role assigned. Access to calculate payments for the Fulltime class and assigns the role for the Employee.
    Author:
    Muhammad Faizan Saiyed, Michael Neustater
